	<article id="post-3600" class="post-3600 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-civil-liberties category-democracy category-intelligence category-interviews category-privacy-2 category-surveillance tag-30c3 tag-ccc tag-france-inter tag-interview tag-privacy tag-radio-2 tag-surveillance-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
