	<article id="post-1896" class="post-1896 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-civil-liberties category-democracy category-intelligence category-interviews category-media category-mi5 category-national-security category-osa category-spies category-torture category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-accountability-2 tag-civil-liberties-2 tag-free-speech-debate tag-intelligence-2 tag-mi5 tag-national-security-2 tag-osa tag-spies-2 tag-whistleblowers-2 tag-wikileaks">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/thefree-speech-debate.html" title="Permalink to The Free Speech Debate" rel="bookmark">The Free Speech Debate</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/thefree-speech-debate.html" title="14:39" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-12-04T14:39:25+00:00" pubdate>December 4, 2012</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/thefree-speech-debate.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>My recent inter­view for the excel­lent Oxford Uni­ver­sity <a href="http://freespeechdebate.com/en/">Free Speech Debate</a> pro­ject, run by Pro­fessor Timothy Gar­ton Ash.  I dis­cuss whis­tleblow­ing, the Offi­cial Secrets Act, Wikileaks and much more:</p>
<p><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/54842651" frameborder="0" width="500" height="281"></iframe></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/thefree-speech-debate.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
